data.description: This gorgeous home has all the space you could ever need in a great location! It is a 5 bedroom and 3 bathroom approx. 2351sqft property with a glass and midnigh blue pebble, salt system pool and spa. The main bedroom features a double glass door that leads into the pool, spa and backyard. The main bathroom has a double sink and separate shower and tub; in addition, it has a spacious walk in closet. The kitchen shows off stunning black granite counters, stainless steel appliances, island with bar stools and opens up to the dinning and breakfast area that has a fireplace which all overlook the pool and stunning mountain views. Throughout the house, there are modern ceiling fans that have been upgraded.The patio is perfect for out door adventures under the sun like hosting bbqs with the built in BBQ that includes seating area for easy entertainment. This home includes a laundry room and a two car garage. You can find this house in Las Colinas gated community with low HOA fees of $125. It is about 5 minutes way from the 10 freeway, a few minutes away from Highway 111, and is close to grocery and shopping areas, restaurants and more! This property is one off a kind and is just missing you.
